  {
    "uuid": "84c6ac90-b586-5a96-90b0-6faef95b381e",
    "entry": "奕世",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "えきせい",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "many generations",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "その家系は、奕世（何世代にもわたり）にわたって酒造業を営んでいる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "この古い寺院は、王朝の興亡を見守りながら、奕世（何世代にもわたり）建ち続けている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼女の家族の遺産は、地域の歴史に深く根ざし、奕世（何世代にもわたり）続いている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": [
            {
              "text": "世祖大明六年、詔曰、倭王世子興、奕世載忠、作藩外海、禀化寧境、恭修貢職、新嗣邊業、宜授爵號、可安東將軍・倭國王。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "宋書倭國傳",
                "author": "沈約",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
